nglish football|1959\u201360]]\n|First Division\n|41||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||42||0\n|-\n|[[1960\u201361 in English football|1960\u201361]]\n|First Division\n|40||0||4||0||2||0||46||0\n|-\n|[[1961\u201362 in English football|1961\u201362]]\n|First Division\n|40||0||2||0||1||0||43||0\n|-\n|[[1962\u201363 in English football|1962\u201363]]\n|First Division\n|15||0||0||0||1||0||16||0\n|-\n|[[1963\u201364 in English football|1963\u201364]]\n|Second Division\n|3||0||0||0||0||0||3||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Total\n!508!!0!!33!!0!!4!!0!!545!!0\n|-\n|[[Telford United F.C.|Wellington Town]]\n|[[1964\u201365 in English football|1964\u201365]]\n|[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]\n|2||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||2||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Total\n!2!!0!!0!!0!!colspan=\"2\"|\u2014!!2!!0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!553!!0!!35!!0!!4!!0!!592!!0\n|}\n<small>Sources: Rowlands, ''Trautmann: The Biography'', p.&nbsp;252; James, ''Manchester City: The Complete Record'', pp.&nbsp;367\u2013395.</small>\n\n==Honours==\n;Manchester City\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[1956 FA Cup Final|1956]]\n\n;Individual\n*[[Iron Cross First Class]]: 1942\n*[[FWA Footballer of the Year]]: 1956\n*[[English Football Hall of Fame]]: 2005\n*[[Germany's Sports Hall of Fame]]: 2011\n*[[Order of Merit of the Federal Republic of Germany]]: 1997\n*[[Order of the British Empire]]: 2004\n\n==References==\n\n===Notes===\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n===Bibliography===\n{{refbegin}}\n*{{cite book |last=Trautmann |first=Bert |title=Steppes To Wembley |publisher=Robert Hale Limited |location=London |year=1956}}\n*{{cite book |last=Rowlands |first=Alan |title=Trautmann: The Biography |publisher=Breedon |location=Derby |year=2005 |isbn=1-85983-491-4}}\n*{{cite book |last= James|first= Gary| title= The Official Manchester City Hall of Fame |publisher= Hamlyn |year= 2005 |isbn= 0-600-61282-1}}\n*{{cite book |last=James |first=Gary |title=Manchester City: The Complete Record |publisher=Breedon |location=Derby |year=2006 |isbn=1